<ab facs="#facs_341_r1l15">vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_341_r1l17"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Steffans Reten / . <expan>ſı<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> </ab>
