</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_341" id="170r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> Ernst und
                            <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, es hat Hilpolt
                                <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etwivil hab <expan>un<ex>d</ex></expan>
                        kaufmanschaft <expan>aufgehalt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und gen Prunne gefüret,
                        darumb wir im <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und unser
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bey im gehabt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und ist den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das ire noch nicht
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und er hat das getan in den dingen, daz wir
                        nicht wissen, daz wir mit im <expan>cze schicke<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dann lieb und güt, und sein des von im
                        unbesorgt <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir in von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daran weisen wöllet, daz er den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das ir wider geb. Und tüt
                                <expan>daryn<ex>n</ex>e</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. und das
                        <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>similit<ex>er</ex></expan>. <expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Abtsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>hofmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, und
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Steffans reten
                                <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.
                            <expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>it<ex>em</ex></expan> herczog Ludwigs
                        reten <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>
<expan>mitname<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen <expan>Gumppenberg<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>Seicze<ex>n</ex></expan> Marschalk und
                                <expan>Wyeland<ex>en</ex></expan> Swelher.</ab>
</div>
